<seg id="76">In November 2003, held a coordination meeting, at which it was inter alia agreed on the selection of commodities - goods, which accounted for a significant risk when compliance with customs and tax regulations: - alcohol and spirits, items of the customs tariff no. 2207 and 2208, - tobacco and tobacco products, items customs tariff heading no 2401, 2402 and 2403, - computers and computer components, items and sub-items of the customs tariff heading no 8471 and 8473 30, - mobile phones and their accessories, the subheading of the customs tariff no 8525 20 91, 8525 20 99, 8529 90 40.</seg>
