<seg id="31">2. Recap of control results</seg>
<seg id="32">2.1. Evaluation of control activities</seg>
<seg id="33">The subject of parallel checks was: - asylum process, - asylum facilities, - management of state funds and property, - internal control system.</seg>
<seg id="34">Mutual exchange of gained experience among the Supreme audit office, Czech republic and Najvyšším kontrolným úradom of the Slovak republic took place at the stage of preparation and implementation of the control actions.</seg>
