<seg id="67">The supreme audit office, Czech republic and Najvyšší kontrolný úrad Slovak republic despite some identified weaknesses, evaluates positively the procedure of RFA and MOO in the delivery of services to asylum seekers.</seg>
<seg id="68">On the basis of the knowledge obtained in the course of inspection, the Supreme audit office, Czech republic and Najvyšší kontrolný úrad of the Slovak republic state that despite the significant increase in the number of asylum seekers in recent years the relevant departments of the two countries made the tasks associated with the care of asylum seekers at an appropriate level.</seg>
