<seg id="50">GERMANY and the CZECH republic have concluded in the year 2000, the Treaty between the Federal republic of Germany and the Czech republic, linking the German highway And 17 and the Czech motorway D 8 on the common state border through the construction of the frontier bridge.</seg>
