<seg id="117">The european parliament and the Council of the European union take to ensure free competition in the EU, inter alia, the directive on the coordination of procedures for the award of public contracts for public works, supplies and services with the aim of ensuring the free movement of goods and services and the directive on the coordination of laws, regulations and administrative provisions relating to review procedures concerning the award of public supply contracts and public works contracts (directive on review procedures), with these two directives should be transposed into national law.</seg>
