<seg id="25">(CZ) the Aim of the control action in the Czech republic was to examine the procedure of the financial authorities in the administration of value added tax after the integration of the Czech republic to the single internal market of the European union (hereinafter "EU") united with the free movement of goods and services, and explore the use of VIES, in particular in monitoring the application of the right to exemption from value added tax in intrakomunitárního delivery.</seg>
