<seg id="845">While in the Czech Republic the payers reported electricity supply in accordance with the applicable text of Act No. 235/2004 Coll. as the intracommunity supply of goods, from the point of view of the German legal regulations valid in 2004, this was not an intracommunity acquisition, but a taxable supply with the place of implementation implementation on the territory of the federal republic of GERMANY.</seg>
