<seg id="850">Therefore, Czech payers should not have provided electricity to SH in 2005.</seg>
<seg id="851">By reporting intracommunitary electricity supply in SH, the two above-mentioned payers distorted the VIES data by a total of CZK 503 881 939 (EUR 16 917 873).</seg>
<seg id="852">Conclusion</seg>
<seg id="853">Cooperation has met the objectives of the BRH and the Sao.</seg>
