<seg id="73">For the transport of other excise products (mineral oil, wine and beer) in the period from 1. May 2004 to 31. December 2005 (hereinafter referred to as "controlled period") the taxpayer had an obligation to notify the Customs office Poprad, respectively. the competent customs office of the initiation of the transport in the regime of conditional exemption from tax.</seg>
