<seg id="89">2.3. registration of traffic opened and completed by the customs authorities in the Czech Republic and the Czech Republic</seg>
<seg id="90">A single electronic system is not in place to monitor the transport of goods under the conditional exemption scheme between the member states of the European Union.</seg>
