<seg id="100">3. Preparation and course of cooperation</seg>
<seg id="101">The first coordination meeting of representatives of the Sao-CR and representatives of the Sao-SR, which discussed the specific procedure for cooperation in the implementation of parallel controls in the field of excise duties, took place in January 2006.</seg>
