<seg id="104">At the meeting it was agreed that the Czech and the Slovak side of the: - process the total data on the quantity of excisable products being transported from the CZECH republic to SLOVAKIA and vice versa, whose transport was initiated in the audited period, - comparing the data on the dopravách mineral oils - combined nomenclature code 2710 and 2711, and alcohol - combined nomenclature code 2207 and 2208 in the regime of conditional exemption from the levy initiated in the CZECH republic and completed in the SR and on the contrary, in the months of November 2004 and September 2005.</seg>
